fields.name: PRS Private Stock, Chesapeake Bay Bridge #PS9620
fields.description: The PRS Ltd Edition Private Stock is the best of the best. All the premium woods which make it up have been hand selected from PRS's legendary Private Stock vault, which contains the finest woods you'll ever lay eyes on. It all starts with the curly maple which has been used for the top of this guitar. Rare and beautiful, this luscious wood offers incredible grain patterns which accentuate the pristine, professional-grade finish. And African ribbon mahogany makes up the back, providing a solid, seamless foundation for this guitar's looks and tone. This is far more than just a guitar - it's a piece of art.

fields.name: Ibanez PIA3761, Stallion White
fields.description: Unrivalled performance. Visionary style. A masterclass in both. To quote Steve Vai, the Ibanez PIA3761 is 'one of the best instruments in the universe.' Alongside breath taking good looks, this legendary axe gives you full access to fierce tonal textures, going from gritty bite to vicious crunch with just pick attack alone. Join one of the biggest guitar heroes on the planet, and unlock infinite creative freedom.
